==================================================
IMPORTANT DISTINCTIONS
==================================================

You must distinguish carefully between:

1. AI vs classic automation
Do not use AI where deterministic automation is better.

2. API automation vs computer use
Prefer APIs where available.
Use browser/computer use only when necessary.

3. Recommendation vs execution
Some workflows should produce suggestions only.
Others can safely automate actions.

4. Assistive vs autonomous
Some tasks should stay human-led with AI help.
Others can be agent-led with approvals.

5. Quick wins vs strategic builds
Do not flatten all opportunities into one bucket.

